nk>https://zenn.dev/genda_jp/articles/b7fe56ce2fc60f</link><description>[score: 0.898] &lt;blockquote cite="https://zenn.dev/genda_jp/articles/b7fe56ce2fc60f" title="Codexを使い始めて長時間稼働させるまで"&gt;&lt;cite&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn-ak2.favicon.st-hatena.com/64?url=https%3A%2F%2Fzenn.dev%2Fgenda_jp%2Farticles%2Fb7fe56ce2fc60f" /&gt; &lt;a href="https://zenn.dev/genda_jp/articles/b7fe56ce2fc60f"&gt;Codexを使</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://zenn.dev/genda_jp/articles/b7fe56ce2fc60f</guid><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 20:28:53 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>気候テック「冬の時代」になぜエネ企業のIPOが相次ぐのか？</title><link>https://www.technologyreview.jp/s/383874/climate-tech-companies-are-going-public-whats-next/</link><description>[score: 0.898] &lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="AP24177191447994-1400x787.jpg" src="https://www.technologyreview.jp/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2026/05/AP24177191447994-1400x787.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;気候テックへの連邦支援が打ち切られる米トランプ政権下で、地熱・原子力・太陽光の3社が相次いでIPOを果たした。データセンターの急拡大が電力需要を押し上げ、グーグルやアマゾンを後ろ盾に持つエネルギー企業に、投資家の資金が集まっている。</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.technologyreview.jp/s/383874/climate-tech-companies-are-going-public-whats-next/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 21:29:02 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>15万スター超のCLAUDE.mdに学ぶ、Claude Codeを暴走させない運用術</title><link>https://qiita.com/4q_sano/items/dc26f7468dcd39fbe62f?utm_campaign=popular_items&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=popular_items</link><description>[score: 0.899] &lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="https%3A%2F%2Fqiita-user-contents.imgix." src="https://qiita-user-contents.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fqiita-user-contents.imgix.net%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fcdn.qiita.com%252Fassets%252Fpublic%252Farticle-ogp-background-afbab5eb44e0b055cce1258705637a91.png%3Fixlib%3Drb-4.1.1%26w%3D1200%26blen</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://qiita.com/4q_sano/items/dc26f7468dcd39fbe62f?utm_campaign=popular_items&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=popular_items</guid><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 08:24:29 +0000</pubDate></it